# Committed build artifacts. dist/ is tracked (hosts install from a release tag
# = the git tree, with no node_modules — see .claude/rules/build-and-entries.md),
# but it is generated, non-reproducible (esbuild content-hashed chunks), and
# never hand-edited. Mark it so:
#   linguist-generated  → GitHub collapses it in PR diffs + excludes it from
#                         language stats and code search.
#   -diff               → git suppresses textual diffs (one-line summaries in
#                         PRs and locally; fewer content-hash merge conflicts).
# dist stays fully tracked and shippable; only its display changes.
plugins/*/dist/** linguist-generated=true -diff
packages/*/dist/** linguist-generated=true -diff
